        <li>We are solving the classic philosophical problem of what Hogwarts House one would be placed in by the great and wise Sorting Hat. To that end, our group created the gitSorted app. While the Sorting Hat would magically have access to who you are, we as developers have to go through the muggle route of having 5 questions that we ask the participant. Each question will have 5 options one can select from. Once we have the required information we are then able to use our muggle coding powers to sort the participant into their Hogwarts House.
        </li>
  
        <li>
